OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F445A1777727463
OL,3,CConservatives apologise for Bloody
OL,4,CSunday footage use over Army veteran
OL,5,Csupport
OL,7,FThe Conservative Party has apologised
OL,8,Ffor a social media video of its leader
OL,9,Fcalling for support for Army veterans
OL,10,Falongside footage from Bloody Sunday.
OL,12,FThe video, criticising the Northern
OL,13,FIreland Troubles Bill, was posted to
OL,14,Fleader Kemi Badenoch's social media
OL,15,Fchannels on Tuesday and removed on
OL,16,FFriday.
OL,18,FIt featured footage of Mrs Badenoch
OL,19,Fcondemning the Bill and was overlaid,
OL,20,Fin part, with archive clips of British
OL,21,Fsoldiers.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G1/8
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
