OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,446,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44502
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F445A1777727463
OL,3,CConservatives apologise for Bloody
OL,4,CSunday footage use over Army veteran
OL,5,Csupport
OL,7,FAt least one of the shots was
OL,8,Fidentified by Foyle MP Colum Eastwood
OL,9,Fas having been filmed on Bloody
OL,10,FSunday. He described its use as
OL,11,F"disgusting" and "disgraceful". He
OL,12,Fsaid it was a departure from previous
OL,13,FConservative leader and Prime Minister
OL,14,FDavid Cameron's apology for Bloody
OL,15,FSunday.
OL,17,FHe said the actions of the Parachute
OL,18,FRegiment were 'unjustified and
OL,19,Funjustifiable'.
OL,26,@sD@AOUsD@LO]sD@ROUsD@^O]
