PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F445A1777727463
OL,3,CConservatives apologise for Bloody
OL,4,CSunday footage use over Army veteran
OL,5,Csupport
OL,7,FIn 2010, then Conservative prime
OL,8,Fminister David Cameron apologised to
OL,9,Fthe families of the civil rights
OL,10,Fmarchers killed on Bloody Sunday after
OL,11,Fthe Saville Inquiry found all were
OL,12,Finnocent.
OL,14,FThe SDLP MP, Colum Eastwood told UTV:
OL,15,F"It's utterly appalling. Kemi Badenoch
OL,16,Fhas put up a video using images of the
OL,17,Fsoldiers of Bloody Sunday going in to
OL,18,Fmurder people on Bloody Sunday as a
OL,19,Fsort of supportive video for veterans.
OL,26,@wD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G4/8
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,446,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44505
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F445A1777727463
OL,3,CConservatives apologise for Bloody
OL,4,CSunday footage use over Army veteran
OL,5,Csupport
OL,7,F"It just shows you all that she's
OL,8,Fabout, all that the Tories are about.
OL,9,FThey don't care about victims. It's
OL,10,Fextremely insensitive.
OL,12,F"They've now taken the video down
OL,13,Funder the pressure that I think we've
OL,14,Fput them under, but they owe an
OL,15,Fapology to the Bloody Sunday victims,
OL,16,Fthe families who have been left behind
OL,17,Fwho have had to struggle for simple
OL,18,Ftruth over a long many years.
OL,20,F"It's important now that Kemi Badenoch
OL,21,Fapologises to them."
OL,26,@oD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G5/8
