OL,3,CConservatives apologise for Bloody
OL,4,CSunday footage use over Army veteran
OL,5,Csupport
OL,7,FIn the video, Mrs Badenoch said
OL,8,FLabour's Bill will "drag" Troubles
OL,9,Fveterans back to court.
OL,11,F"It will put elderly veterans through
OL,12,Ffresh legal battles at the end of
OL,13,Ftheir lives," she said.
OL,15,FMrs Badenoch said her party will "vote
OL,16,Fto block" the legislation and "a
OL,17,Ffuture Conservative government will
OL,18,Frepeal it" and posted a link to a
OL,19,Fpetition to stop the Bill.
OL,26,@pD@TOUpD@YO]sD@AOUuD@MO]wD@bOUxD@IO]xD@
