OL,3,CConservatives apologise for Bloody
OL,4,CSunday footage use over Army veteran
OL,5,Csupport
OL,7,FThe Northern Ireland Troubles Bill was
OL,8,Fdesigned to repeal and replace the
OL,9,Fcontroversial Legacy Act introduced by
OL,10,Fthe previous Conservative government,
OL,11,Fending the immunity scheme brought in
OL,12,Funder the law, which was ruled
OL,13,Funlawful in the courts.
OL,15,FCatch up with the latest UTV Live on
OL,16,FITVX
OL,18,FSign up for our free weekly newsletter
OL,19,Fhere.
